data.description:
This home sits on just under 40 acres, the land is fenced and cross fenced. There is a 24x20 two (2) car garage, a metal garage/workshop that is 28x36 built in 2016.  A 32x56 barn with three (3) 16x14 stalls, tack room also has water and electricity, a 28x30 greenhouse that also has an attached shed.   The exterior of the home and the two (2) car garage have jellyfish lighting that you can customize.

Roof replaced 2023. Heating unit was replaced in 2021. Insulation blown into walls and under home in 2021. 1000-gallon propane tank purchased in 2021. Carpet was replaced in bedrooms in 2020. The five (5) piece master has a newer soaker tub to relax in at the end of the day.  Updated vinyl plank flooring throughout main living area.
